title: "Know Ye Not That So Many of Us as Were Baptized into Jesus Christ Were Baptized into His Death" («Nous...c'est en Sa mort que nous avons été baptisé»), plate XXX from Miserere
medium: Aquatint over photogravure from an illustrated book with 22 aquatints over photogravure (19 with drypoint, 18 with roulette, five with etching)
